Subject: Re: [VB] Are 67's supposed to have reverse lights??

Reverse lights started mid-year '67.  My '67 doesn't have reverse lights,
and it was produced on Dec. 5th.  I'm not sure when exactly they started,
but it was obviously sometime after that.

